# 非洲为苏丹问题召开首场首脑级会议  喀土穆发出威胁

Author: 半岛电视台＋通讯社

Publisher: Al Jazeera

Published Time: 2023-05-27T14:04:04

Modified Time: 2023-05-27T14:04:04

Description: 非盟和平与安全理事会将于27日召开国家元首和政府首脑级会议，以讨论苏丹当前的危机，与此同时，苏丹军队与快速支援部队之间的前线保持着谨慎的平静。

Images: ["[RTSIRB3Q-1685...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/RTSIRB3Q-1685178959.jpg)", "[image-1685195...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/image-1685195559.jpg)", "[image-1-16851...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/image-1-1685195616.jpg)", "[image-413-168...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/image-413-1685158441.jpg)"]

